cs.LG, cs.CV, cs.CR, cs.AI, cs.NE 

This paper is likely to belong to the sub-category of machine learning (cs.LG) as it deals with adversarial attacks on classifiers. It also involves computer vision (cs.CV) as it pertains to image classification. The paper also discusses the security aspect of the classifiers (cs.CR) and the use of artificial intelligence (cs.AI) in generating certificates. Finally, the paper proposes a new attack method that involves neural networks (cs.NE).
